Tell me

42
00:03:36,870 --> 00:03:38,210
about Lunar Sect.

43
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:41,590
Big Brother

44
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:43,390
is a scholar.

45
00:03:44,110 --> 00:03:45,950
The Fox is a troublemaker.

46
00:03:47,230 --> 00:03:48,410
I thought

47
