55
00:04:07,830 --> 00:04:08,960
You even threatened

56
00:04:09,190 --> 00:04:10,190
to kill me.

57
00:04:15,040 --> 00:04:15,960
After that,

58
00:04:17,220 --> 00:04:19,060
