86
00:06:45,159 --> 00:06:46,909
You chose to weaken your cultivation

87
00:06:46,909 --> 00:06:48,250
to fight against me.

88
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:51,100
But the realm of the Bone-Deep Mirror

89
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:52,380
belongs to me.

90
