93
00:07:21,140 --> 00:07:22,280
Have they all been

94
00:07:22,310 --> 00:07:23,860
killed by you?

95
00:07:28,820 --> 00:07:30,750
I misunderstood you, Dragon Lord.

96
00:07:40,100 --> 00:07:40,830
Dragon Lord.

97
00:07:41,090 --> 00:07:42,490
