101
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:18,820
Ji Yang!

102
00:08:24,610 --> 00:08:25,360
Ji Yang.

103
00:08:31,340 --> 00:08:32,159
Ji Yang!

104
00:09:28,810 --> 00:09:29,580
Yun Nian!

105
00:09:39,830 --> 00:09:41,750
I can't hold on anymore!

